ium/inside-netanyahus-masterplan-to-dismantle-the-freedom-of-the-press-in-israel/00000190-df02-d041-a3f4-ffee92ca0000</guid></item><item><title>谁是卡塔尔文件事件的幕后黑手，以 20 万欧元出售针对内塔尼亚胡的“证据”？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-people-behind-the-qatar-documents-affair-selling-evidence-against-netanyahu/00000190-dabc-d9bf-a195-ffbc14fb0000</link><description>据称证明卡塔尔向内塔尼亚胡提供资金的耸人听闻的出版物背后隐藏着一个以每页数万美元出售可疑文件的网络</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:45:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-people-behind-the-qatar-documents-affair-selling-evidence-against-netanyahu/00000190-dabc-d9bf-a195-ffbc14fb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队证实，两名哈马斯指挥官在西岸图尔卡姆袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-two-hamas-commanders-killed-in-tul-karm-strike-in-west-bank/00000190-dedc-d041-a3f4-fffeee020000</link><description>以色列军方表示，自战争爆发以来，他们在该市发动了约 50 次空袭，最近的行动目的是应对爆炸装置的威胁</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-confirms-two-hamas-commanders-killed-in-tul-karm-strike-in-west-bank/00000190-dedc-d041-a3f4-fffeee020000</guid></item><item><title>圣经前以色列使用昆虫制成的早期红色染料</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-23/ty-article/early-red-dye-made-from-insects-used-in-pre-biblical-israel/00000190-dea5-d851-afbe-dfa5cf560000</link><description>死海头骨洞中发现的数百件织物碎片可以追溯到红铜并用时代到罗马时期，其中一些是惊人的猩红色</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:37:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-23/ty-article/early-red-dye-made-from-insects-used-in-pre-biblical-israel/00000190-dea5-d851-afbe-dfa5cf560000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的公务飞机首飞飞往华盛顿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-official-plan